      <title>当市场称重贸易战时，黄金持有收益，美国衰退风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/gold-xauusd-holds-gain-as-markets-weigh-trade-war-us-recession-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[戈尔德（Gold）在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的on-On-Off关税计划中鞭打了避风港之后，在避风港的支持下，戈尔德（Gold）提前了，他的最新评论低估了对经济衰退的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/gold-xauusd-holds-gain-as-markets-weigh-trade-war-us-recession-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 00:23:35 GMT</pubDate>
